# Qatar Visitor Arrivals Analysis

## 📌 Overview
This project analyzes visitor arrival trends in Qatar using data from `qatar_visitor_arrivals.csv`.  
The analysis includes data cleaning, visualization, and insights extraction.

## 📊 Features
- Reads and cleans visitor arrival data.
- Generates a **line graph** of total visitor arrivals over time.
- Finds **highest & lowest visitor months**.
- Creates a **report with key insights**.
- Saves all results in the `Reports` folder.

